  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Season the chicken with cumin, chili powder, salt, and pepper.",
    "In a large bowl, toss the chicken with rapeseed oil and roast in the oven for 30 minutes.",
    "While the chicken is cooking, toss the onion, red bell pepper, and zucchini with a little bit of rapeseed oil and roast in the oven for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the chicken from the oven and let it rest for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "Add the sliced chicken back to the bowl with the roasted vegetables and stir in the lime juice and coconut cream.",
    "Toss in some chopped cilantro if desired."
